14003157/http://www.cmt.com/news/1747110/kelly-clarkson-im-long-winded-youre-welcome/ |title=Kelly Clarkson: \"I'm Long-Winded. You're Welcome.\" |first=Alison |last=Bonaguro |work=[[CMT (U.S. TV channel)|CMT]] |publisher=[[Viacom Media Networks]] |date=December 23, 2014 |accessdate=August 14, 2015 |archivedate=August 14, 2015}}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"The Hollywood Reporter 1\">\n{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/kelly-clarkson-announces-holiday-benefit-740348 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018202627/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/idol-worship/kelly-clarkson-announces-holiday-benefit-740348 |title=Kelly Clarkson Invites Superstars to Miracle on Broadway |first=Michele |last=Amabile Angermiller |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |publisher=Prometheus Global Media |date=October 13, 2014 |accessdate=October 18, 2014 |archivedate=October 18, 2014}}\n</ref>\n<ref name=\"ABC News Radio 1\">\n{{cite web|url=http://abcnewsradioonline.com/music-news/2015/9/8/kelly-clarkson-schedules-second-annual-christmas-benefit-sho.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150908222530/http://abcnewsradioonline.com/music-news/2015/9/8/kelly-clarkson-schedules-second-annual-christmas-benefit-sho.html |title=Kelly Clarkson Schedules Second Annual Christmas Benefit Show for December |first=Andrea |last=Dresdale |work=[[ABC News Radio]] |publisher=[[American Broadcasting Company]] |date=October 13, 2014 |accessdate=September 8, 2015 |archivedate=September 8, 2015 |url-status=dead }}\n</ref>\n\n}}\n\n== Further reading ==\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.tennessean.com/story/money/2014/11/27/nashville-knows-give-back/19556631/ |title=Nashville knows how to give back |first=John |last=Huber |work=The Tennesean |publisher=Gannett Company  |date=November 27, 2014 |accessdate=August 14, 2015}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.musicrow.com/2014/12/industry-pics-kelly-clarkson-bmi-swon-brothers-love-and-theft/ |title=Industry Pics: Kelly Clarkson, BMI, Swon Broth